    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Edelweiss Knights is a run-based strategy RPG with Visual Novel storytelling that revisits genre classics into a quick-paced yet surprisingly deep experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead a party of 3 Knights in a struggle against godly armies. Buff your team in battle by baking pastries, and forge pacts with almighty Deities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avoid Divine Fury</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deities ominously oversee the battlefield and judge your actions. Use Spell types that trigger them and prepare to face ultimate judgment! Or prepare delicious treats to bond with them and strenghten your Party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/181a769d88acec103f97bc74ebbf4491.poster.avif?t=1769166631\" width=720 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/181a769d88acec103f97bc74ebbf4491.webm?t=1769166631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/181a769d88acec103f97bc74ebbf4491.mp4?t=1769166631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Novel SRPG Approach </strong><br> Mix and match different Units with melee and magic attacks, along with unique environmental abilities, such as placing traps, or push and pulling enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/a36f0667b00a5bd817651e1404043d8b.poster.avif?t=1769166631\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/a36f0667b00a5bd817651e1404043d8b.webm?t=1769166631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/a36f0667b00a5bd817651e1404043d8b.mp4?t=1769166631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the fight goes on, you unlock new VN-style dialogues that deepen the bonds between the three Knights: the champion of faith Edelweiss, the level-headed scientist Aliza and the war hero Violet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/efb556ef7946be8c23022e311c063fbe.poster.avif?t=1769166631\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/efb556ef7946be8c23022e311c063fbe.webm?t=1769166631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3200470/extras/efb556ef7946be8c23022e311c063fbe.mp4?t=1769166631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
